    / *Full Citation:*: Kaelberer MM, Buchanan KL, Klein ME, Barth BB, Montoya MM, Shen X, Bohórquez DV. A gut-brain neural circuit for nutrient sensory transduction. _Science_. 2018;361(6408):eaat5236.
