=== Takizawa et al.\ 2020 — HSC Protection from Stress-Induced Exhaustion

    / *Full Citation:*: Takizawa H, Boettcher S, Manz MG. Protection of hematopoietic stem cells from stress-induced exhaustion and aging. _Experimental Hematology_. 2020;85:1–5.
