    / *Full Citation:*: Stanojcic M, Chen P, Xiu F, Jeschke MG. Impaired Immune Response in Elderly Burn Patients: New Insights Into the Immune-senescence Phenotype. _Annals of Surgery_. 2016;264(1):195--202.
