    / *Study Design:*: Questionnaire development and validation (5 rounds of web surveys + test-retest)
    / *Sample Size:*: Norwegian sample n=1,263 ME/CFS + 178 HC; international English sample n=1,387 ME/CFS
    / *Key Findings:*:
